704127f-a.title: Brooklyn: Emmons Avenue - 29th Street (East)
704127f-a.text:
Emmons Avenue, north side, between East 29th Street and
Nostrand Avenue. Shown is a row of bungalows, which appear on
Hyde's 1929 map as Nos. 1 to 15 Cantor Avenue, the latter evi-
dently being the stretch of low land in front of the dwellings.
June 13, 1940
L. Sperr
